body: Kolkheti National Park Photo Gallery          Ranger shelter on Paliastomi Lake with the Caucasian mountain range in the background.        Point Reyes National Seashore has established a sister park relationship with Kolkheti National Park in the Republic of Georgia. Located in on the coast of the Black Sea, Kolkheti National Park protects an interesting variety of landscapes, flora, and fauna. Visit our Sister Parks page to learn more.                   Kolkheti National Park   17 Photos  Photos from Kolkheti National Park, Republic of Georgia                        Top of Page
